---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy — AgentQuilt">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 28px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--fg)">
    <a href="/" style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none">&larr; agentquilt.dev</a>

    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,38px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin:32px 0 12px">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 40px">Last updated: July 6, 2026</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">What data we collect</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      agentquilt.dev is a static marketing site. We do not use cookies, collect personal data, or operate any user accounts or sign-up forms.
    </p>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      We use <a href="https://vercel.com/analytics" style="color:var(--accent)">Vercel Analytics</a> to count page views and understand which pages are visited. Vercel Analytics is cookieless and does not track individuals across sessions or sites. The data collected (page URL, referrer, browser type, country) is aggregated and not linked to any personally identifiable information. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" style="color:var(--accent)">Vercel's Privacy Policy</a> for details on how they handle this data.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">Third-party requests</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      Fonts are self-hosted and served from the same origin. The GitHub star count is fetched at build time by our server, not by your browser. Page views are reported to Vercel Analytics (see above).
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">Local storage</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      We store one key (<span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:.9em;color:var(--fg)">aq-theme</span>) in your browser's <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:.9em;color:var(--fg)">localStorage</span> to remember your dark/light theme preference. This data never leaves your device.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">Hosting infrastructure</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      The site is hosted on <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" style="color:var(--accent)">Vercel</a>. Vercel may log standard web server data (IP address, request path, timestamp) as part of infrastructure operation. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" style="color:var(--accent)">Vercel's Privacy Policy</a> for details.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">External links</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      Links to GitHub, npm, and other third-party sites are subject to those services' own privacy policies. Clicking an external link will send your IP address to that service.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 10px">Contact</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 16px">
      Questions? Open an issue at <a href="https://github.com/daxdue/agentquilt/issues" style="color:var(--accent)">github.com/daxdue/agentquilt</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
